<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f5; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 16px; }
    .header h1 { color: #ff9800; margin: 0; }
    .content p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #333; }
    .coupon-box { text-align: center; background-color: #fff3e0; border: 2px dashed #ffb74d; padding: 20px; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #e65100; letter-spacing: 2px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 8px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #888; margin-top: 30px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Hangout Cafe</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <strong><%= userName %></strong>,</p>
      <p>Your recent order (<strong>#<%= orderId %></strong>) has been cancelled and refunded as requested.</p>
      <p>Since your payment was securely processed, we have issued a refund directly via a Cafe Coupon Code for the total amount of <strong>₹<%= amount %></strong>. You can instantly apply this code on your next visit or online order!</p>
      <div class="coupon-box">
        <%= couponCode %>
      </div>
      <p>This code does not expire. Make sure to keep it safe!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; 2026 Hangout Cafe. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
